,"class_list":["post-19209","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-faith-iman","tag-blessing-al-barakah","tag-clothing-al-malabis","tag-community-jamaah","tag-companions-sahaba","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-manners-adab","tag-paradise-jannah","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-righteous-predecessors-salaf-as-salih","tag-travel-al-safr","tag-unseen-al-ghayb","tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4ZP","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33435,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/blessed-faith-without-seeing\/","url_meta":{"origin":19209,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Blessed is one who has faith without seeing him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman al-Juhani reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what do you think of one who has faith in you, believes in you, and follows you, but never saw you?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe is blessed. Again, he is blessed.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18301,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/28\/blessed-who-believed-never-saw-him\/","url_meta":{"origin":19209,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Blessed are those who never saw him but believed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBlessed are those who had faith in me and saw me, and blessed seven times are those who had faith in me and never saw me.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 12578 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26054,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/12\/blessed-content-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":19209,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Contentment: Blessed is one satisfied with Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 12, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn 'Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBlessed is one who is guided to Islam, whose livelihood is sufficient, and who is content with what he has.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2349 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24976,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/08\/kab-moses-merciful-creation\/","url_meta":{"origin":19209,"position":3},"title":"Ka\u2019b on Mercy: Blessed are those who are merciful to creation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b reported: Allah Almighty said to Moses, upon him be peace, \u201cO Moses, be soft in nature, for the most abhorred creation to me is one within whom is arrogance, in whose tongue is sharpness, and in whose heart is hardness. The most beloved character traits to me are mercy,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35117,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/01\/tuba-faults\/","url_meta":{"origin":19209,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Humility: Blessed is one busy with self-improvement","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBlessed is he who is occupied with his own faults over the faults of people.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 6237 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645 \u0637\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24327,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/01\/abu-sulaiman-ikhlaas-step\/","url_meta":{"origin":19209,"position":5},"title":"Abu Sulayman on Ikhlaas: Blessed are those who walk sincerely to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Qudamah reported: Abu Sulayman, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBlessed is he who takes a single step, desiring nothing but Allah Almighty.\u201d Ma\u2019ruf al-Karkhi would strike himself and say, \u201cO my soul! Be sincere and purify yourself!\u201d Source: Minha\u0304j al-Qa\u0304s\u0323di\u0304n 1\/365 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0642\u062f\u0627\u0645\u0629 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u0628\u0648 \u0633\u0644\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19209","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=19209"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19209\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=19209"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=19209"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=19209"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}